-- Pier 1 January same-store sales down
-- 
-- Thu Feb 1, 2007 6:22am EST
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2007/02/01/us-pier1-sales-idUSWNAS924720070201

 

 (Reuters) - Pier 1 Imports Inc. ( PIR.N ) said it recorded a 13.2 percent fall in January sales at stores open for at least a year. 


 In a news release, the home decor retailer said sales also fell 13.7 percent to $110.7 million for the four-week period ended January 27, compared with $128.3 million in the year-ago period. (Reporting by Amitha Rajan in Bangalore)